---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service & Privacy" description="Terms of Service and Privacy Policy for Oak Ridge Roofing Co.">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms of Service & Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Last updated: May 31, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container legal-content">
    <div class="alert-box">
      <strong>Important Notice:</strong> This website is a fictional demonstration created by <a href="https://pageandpixel.com">Page and Pixel</a> for portfolio purposes only. Oak Ridge Roofing Co. is not a real business. No actual services are offered, no orders will be fulfilled, and no payments should be made. This site should not be treated as a real contractor or roofing business.
    </div>

    <h2>Terms of Service</h2>
    
    <h3>1. Acceptance of Terms</h3>
    <p>By accessing and using this website, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and conditions of this agreement.</p>

    <h3>2. Nature of Business</h3>
    <p>Oak Ridge Roofing Co. is a fictional demonstration website created for design portfolio purposes. The services, testimonials, pricing, and company information presented on this website are entirely fictional and do not represent an actual business entity.</p>

    <h3>3. No Real Services</h3>
    <p>This website does not offer any real roofing services, repairs, inspections, or consultations. Any resemblance to actual services, companies, or individuals is purely coincidental and fictional.</p>

    <h3>4. Contact Information</h3>
    <p>If you have any questions about these terms, please contact:</p>
    <p>Page and Pixel<br>
    Email: hello@pageandpixel.com<br>
    Website: https://pageandpixel.com</p>

    <h3>5. Limitation of Liability</h3>
    <p>Under no circumstances shall the creators of this website be held liable for any damages arising from the use of this fictional demonstration site.</p>

    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

    <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>If you choose to interact with our contact form, you may provide personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, and project details. This information is collected solely for demonstration purposes and will not be used, stored, or shared by any real business entity.</p>

    <h3>Use of Information</h3>
    <p>Any information submitted through this website's contact form is fictional and part of the demonstration. No real communications will result from submitting this form.</p>

    <h3>Data Security</h3>
    <p>While we are committed to maintaining reasonable security measures for any demonstration data, this is a fictional site and no actual sensitive personal data should be submitted.</p>

    <h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
    <p>This website may use third-party services for analytics and functionality. These services are used in accordance with their respective privacy policies.</p>

    <h3>Your Rights</h3>
    <p>As this is a demonstration site with no real data collection, no actual user data rights apply. However, you should not submit any real personal information to this website.</p>

    <h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>
    <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of any changes.</p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>This website is a creative work of fiction created for portfolio presentation. Page and Pixel creates demonstration websites for clients and potential clients to showcase design capabilities. This site should not be replicated, distributed, or used for any purpose other than viewing the design work.</p>

    <p>All trademarks, service marks, and trade names appearing on this site are fictional and owned by the fictional Oak Ridge Roofing Co. entity created for this demonstration.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, #4A3E2B 100%);
    color: var(--color-surface);
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 { color: var(--color-surface); margin-bottom: var(--space-4); }
  .hero-subtitle { font-size: var(--font-size-body-lg); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); }

  .section-pad { padding: var(--space-16) 0; }

  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .alert-box {
    background: #FFF3CD;
    border: 1px solid #FFC107;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .alert-box a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    padding-top: var(--space-4);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(93, 78, 55, 0.2);
  }

  .legal-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
  }

  .legal-content h3 {
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .legal-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
</style>
